{"id": "1365375867844431872", "channel_id": "1181152750319456266", "type": 19, "author_id": "776811138984706089", "author_name": "wild_pansy", "author_bot": false, "content": "我是沒算過啦但我玩下來那個傷害差了很多有些時候有手術刀配合蘿坦覺醒能多打100k左右\n但我說的聽聽就好都不準我都是靠感覺而已", "timestamp": "2025-04-25T17:16:14.351000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["655338276554801152"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1365374638745456771", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
